### Variables are defined in http-client.env.json
@baseUrl = localhost/groups

### List all groups
GET {{baseUrl}}
Accept: application/json

### List active groups only
GET {{baseUrl}}/active
Accept: application/json

### Get specific group by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/-1002215169635
Accept: application/json

### Test with the group ID shown in your screenshot
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{GROUP_ID}}
Accept: application/json

### Create or update group (if the API supports this)
POST {{baseUrl}}/create_or_update
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "group_id": -1002215169635,
    "title": "test_bot",
    "is_active": true
}

### Deactivate a group
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{GROUP_ID}}/deactivate
Accept: application/json